You seem to be in good spirits.

0:02:42.040,0:02:43.960
Wenyi whines every day until I bring her out to play.

0:02:44.180,0:02:46.940
This mischievous little goblin gives me a headache.

0:02:47.260,0:02:49.080
Even if they wished for it,

0:02:49.080,0:02:51.180
others couldn't have such a headache.

0:02:51.560,0:02:53.280
Can I hold you for a second?

0:02:53.320,0:02:56.380
Aiya, princess Wenyi, aiya.

0:02:57.480,0:02:58.840
Behave yourself with Concubine Sourire.

0:02:58.980,0:02:59.940
Greet Concubine Sourire.

0:02:59.940,0:03:00.900
Concubine Sourire.

0:03:00.900,0:03:03.020
No worries. It's sweet when
a child isn't shy with strangers.

0:03:03.280,0:03:04.620
Give me a kiss.

0:03:06.240,0:03:07.400
And this side.

0:03:08.720,0:03:11.540
Here, be careful not to crease Your Highness's dress.

0:03:17.100,0:03:18.780
I have something to tell Your Highness.

0:03:21.660,0:03:22.940
It's so beautiful outside in spring.

0:03:22.960,0:03:25.060
I was just going to take a stroll
in the Garden of Dawning Spring.

0:03:25.260,0:03:26.500
Please excuse me.

0:03:27.080,0:03:28.600
I bid Your Highness goodbye.

0:03:42.980,0:03:43.880
Cao.

0:03:45.980,0:03:47.640
You have something to tell me ?

0:03:56.440,0:03:57.720
Having regained her status,

0:03:57.720,0:03:59.920
Consort Fleur summoned me to
the Palace of Earthly Honor yesterday.

0:04:01.060,0:04:02.540
There is nothing wrong with that.

0:04:02.860,0:04:05.300
You have always been close with her.

0:04:05.840,0:04:08.420
Now that her title has been restored,
you should congratulate her.

0:04:09.080,0:04:09.940
Certainly.

0:04:10.100,0:04:11.920
Congratulatory gifts have already been sent.

0:04:12.320,0:04:15.080
However, Consort Fleur asked about

0:04:15.540,0:04:18.840
Your Highness's activities over the
period of her confinement.

0:04:20.620,0:04:22.240
An intelligent woman such as yourself

0:04:22.360,0:04:24.300
can surely respond to her questions with propriety.

0:04:25.100,0:04:26.340
Whatever you say

0:04:26.560,0:04:28.640
depends on your plans for the future, Lady Cao.

0:04:28.980,0:04:30.660
What plans would I have?

0:04:30.920,0:04:33.360
I am just following Your Highnees's lead.

0:04:36.620,0:04:39.520
Still, Consort Fleur was your old master.

0:04:40.060,0:04:43.380
Although she was unkind to you and the princess at times,

0:04:43.760,0:04:46.280
she aided in promoting your status after all.

0:04:46.940,0:04:49.880
Her rank and family background
are far superior to my own.

0:04:50.880,0:04:54.320
It's only natural if you plan to be close to her.

0:04:55.320,0:04:57.960
Your Highness need not speak in riddles.

0:04:58.940,0:05:01.320
Dull-witted as I am, I do know that

0:05:01.640,0:05:03.580
Consort Fleur's regained favor and status

0:05:03.580,0:05:05.600
will pass like the blooming of an orchid cactus.

0:05:05.800,0:05:08.680
She's an arrow approaching the end of its flight.

0:05:09.840,0:05:14.060
I want a peaceful life for Wenyi and myself,
so I won't be taking any risks.

0:05:17.520,0:05:20.200
Cao, you have a perceptive mind and a keen intellect

0:05:20.780,0:05:23.000
to which few people can compare.

0:05:24.620,0:05:27.160
In fact, I do not wish that

0:05:27.240,0:05:29.160
you drift apart from Consort Fleur.

0:05:32.040,0:05:35.120
Since I have entrusted the princess
and myself to Your Highness,

0:05:35.400,0:05:37.700
I will follow only Your Highness's orders.

0:05:38.040,0:05:40.120
Why would I lean towards her?

0:05:41.080,0:05:44.040
I understand Your Highness's request.

0:05:44.560,0:05:46.300
And I will not disappoint Your Highness.

0:05:46.940,0:05:49.000
Cao, you understand when to advance and when to withdraw.

0:05:49.220,0:05:50.480
I have nothing to worry about.

0:05:52.300,0:05:55.200
Since Consort Fleur has inquired about me,

0:05:55.660,0:05:58.960
I will use her same methods against her.

0:06:00.440,0:06:03.660
What are her thoughts about her reinstatement?

0:06:05.760,0:06:07.700
She's been reveling in the feeling of it

0:06:07.700,0:06:10.060
but is also afraid of losing favor again.

0:06:11.200,0:06:12.860
With her previous fall from favor,

0:06:12.900,0:06:15.620
and having heard about what happened to
Consort Astuce and Noble Lady Fuca,

0:06:16.360,0:06:18.620
she is quite wary of Your Highness.

0:06:21.540,0:06:23.800
She's seen me as her arch-enemy for all this time.

0:06:24.460,0:06:26.700
Of course, I view her the same way.

0:06:28.240,0:06:30.680
Your Highness will certainly have ways to deal with her.

0:06:30.920,0:06:33.520
I will do what little I can.

0:06:35.080,0:06:37.020
There is one more thing, however.

0:06:37.360,0:06:41.040
Your Highness and I have no vital interests in common.

0:06:41.760,0:06:44.940
To be vulgar, it's an alliance based on short term interests.

0:06:45.780,0:06:49.020
When our interests no longer align,
we may go our separate ways.

0:06:50.300,0:06:53.600
Given my humble status, I understand that 
I can never contend with Your Highness.

0:06:54.500,0:06:55.800
Therefore,

0:06:57.360,0:07:00.200
I am afraid I may not be of much help to Your Highness.

0:07:01.820,0:07:03.480
Cao, you are refreshingly candid.

0:07:03.480,0:07:05.540
Your concern is the same as my own.

0:07:06.260,0:07:08.540
As of yet, I still do not have any children.

0:07:09.220,0:07:11.300
Princess Wenyi is as fair as jade and snow.

0:07:11.880,0:07:14.640
I would like her to become my
honorary daughter after we succeed

0:07:14.860,0:07:16.940
so we can be each other's support.

0:07:17.320,0:07:18.900
What do you think, Cao?

0:07:20.580,0:07:23.380
If that were to happen, then we all would be at ease.

0:07:24.320,0:07:25.960
Your Highness's prospects are boundless.

0:07:25.960,0:07:29.160
It would be Wenyi's blessing
to receive Your Highness's care.

0:07:32.200,0:07:34.080
Cao, your hairpin looks familiar.

0:07:34.560,0:07:37.160
I saw it in His Majesty's treasury once.

0:07:37.540,0:07:39.400
It must have been granted to you by His Majesty.

0:07:39.400,0:07:41.880
Indeed, but it was just a small gift.

0:07:45.640,0:07:47.600
Cao, you have really beautiful hands.

0:07:48.640,0:07:50.520
Your nails look delicate

0:07:50.740,0:07:52.640
with just some jasmine oil on them.

0:07:53.980,0:07:56.640
But if you painted them with winter jasmine petals,

0:07:56.760,0:08:00.140
this unique touch would surely please His Majesty.

0:08:01.660,0:08:03.720
I thank Your Highness for the advice.

0:08:05.680,0:08:07.800
Dr. Wen, you are leaving in such a rush today.

0:08:07.800,0:08:09.500
You did not even have any tea.

0:08:10.480,0:08:12.480
My Lady, please don't trouble yourself to walk me out.

0:08:12.480,0:08:14.700
Concubine Sourire's herbs are still on the stove.

0:08:15.000,0:08:18.160
I am worried that if the servants lose track of time,
the herbs will lose their effect.

0:08:19.340,0:08:20.780
Is Concubine Sourire ill?

0:08:20.900,0:08:21.780
No,

0:08:22.020,0:08:24.820
they are preparing the Immortal Jade Maiden Powder
for Her Highness's complexion.

0:08:25.080,0:08:27.020
Those young servants are heavy handed

0:08:27.020,0:08:28.980
so I have to watch over it myself.

0:08:29.460,0:08:31.140
I thought it was something urgent.

0:08:31.300,0:08:34.340
His Majesty is very fond of Concubine Sourire right now.

0:08:34.720,0:08:38.580
Given His Majesty's grace, she doesn't need such luxurious face powder.

0:08:39.900,0:08:42.780
Concubine Sourire is at the height of her favor.

0:08:43.360,0:08:45.700
Her doorstep must be weathered from all the visitors.

0:08:46.340,0:08:49.680
I have to keep my distance, even as her sister.

0:08:50.520,0:08:53.980
But sir, you are bustling around to
"sew an extra flower onto her beautiful brocade."

0:08:54.460,0:08:57.320
My Lady, what makes you say that?

0:09:00.720,0:09:04.020
I've been in a foul mood lately.
Please pardon my offense.

0:09:05.040,0:09:08.220
But I know my words are to no avail.

0:09:08.960,0:09:11.000
No one remembers the extra flower sewed on a brocade,

0:09:11.400,0:09:14.380
but charcoal sent on a snowy day touches one's heart deeply.

0:09:15.440,0:09:20.100
Dr. Wen, I believe you understand this well.

0:09:21.560,0:09:23.940
Preparing medicinal herbs is my duty.

0:09:24.380,0:09:28.020
And that's why I also devote myself to your
herb supplies and routine pulse-taking.

0:09:29.140,0:09:31.000
I don't mind "adding a flower to the brocade."

0:09:31.080,0:09:32.360
But I sincerely hope,

0:09:32.360,0:09:34.660
whether it is you or Concubine Sourire,

0:09:34.980,0:09:38.180
that there will never be "a snowy day"
when my skills must be "your charcoal."

0:09:39.320,0:09:43.900
Dr. Wen, I hope that you will see
Sourire and me as equals

0:09:44.640,0:09:46.780
and care for us equally well.

0:09:47.460,0:09:51.540
My Lady, I will attend to the good health
of you and Concubine Sourire.

0:09:52.260,0:09:54.920
Nothing other than this is on my mind.

0:09:57.400,0:09:59.880
Lunar, walk Dr. Wen out.

0:10:00.380,0:10:01.500
Yes, My Lady.

0:10:01.880,0:10:03.240
Take care, Dr. Wen.

0:10:11.040,0:10:12.300
My Lady ...

0:10:15.500,0:10:18.600
Meizhuang, why are you standing outside in the cold?

0:10:18.940,0:10:21.360
You should be careful not to get a cold.

0:10:22.200,0:10:24.800
What brings Your Highness to my humble residence today?

0:10:24.940,0:10:27.780
Don't you need to spend time with His Majesty
to seek favor for Consort Fleur?

0:10:29.700,0:10:31.260
Please don't be angry.

0:10:33.120,0:10:35.140
That's why I come here today.

0:10:35.600,0:10:37.300
Please allow me to explain.

0:10:37.500,0:10:39.280
I'm tired. I want to rest.

0:10:40.020,0:10:41.900
And I need to visit Her Majesty after that.

0:10:42.320,0:10:43.140
Please leave.

0:10:43.540,0:10:45.300
I know you are angry with me,

0:10:46.060,0:10:48.020
but at least allow me a chance to speak.

0:10:48.720,0:10:52.760
Have you lost faith in the years
we spent together as sisters?

0:10:58.640,0:10:59.760
Come in.

0:11:11.720,0:11:14.160
Why is there no one about in your palace?

0:11:15.580,0:11:18.160
Where are the servants? Why aren't they with you?

0:11:20.080,0:11:22.760
The Household Department
is distributing summer clothing today.

0:11:22.760,0:11:24.520
I sent the servants there to collect it.

0:11:25.440,0:11:27.940
It's nothing like your opulent palace

0:11:28.200,0:11:30.060
with crowds rushing forward to serve it.

0:11:30.480,0:11:32.480
The head of the Household Department, Mr. Jiang

0:11:32.480,0:11:35.040
even personally delivers the clothes for your servants.

0:11:36.200,0:11:37.460
I know

0:11:38.060,0:11:40.720
that you don't care about His Majesty's favor.

0:11:43.320,0:11:45.080
Did you say that

0:11:46.040,0:11:48.440
because of Consort Fleur's reinstatement?

0:11:52.920,0:11:55.040
All right, then tell me

0:11:55.620,0:11:58.800
was it you who suggested to
His Majesty to reinstate Consort Fleur?

0:11:59.200,0:12:00.260
Yes.

0:12:00.800,0:12:03.660
But Meizhuang, I was without a choice.

0:12:04.540,0:12:07.420
Who wants to aid the enemy that has killed one's child?

0:12:08.000,0:12:10.180
Think about it from my perspective -

0:12:10.620,0:12:12.360
if it wasn't my only option,

0:12:12.360,0:12:13.940
why would I resort to this?

0:12:14.820,0:12:16.700
Meizhuang, I know you can't bear it,

0:12:16.700,0:12:19.200
but I have endured no less suffering than you.

0:12:20.100,0:12:22.000
Do you think I bear this easily?

0:12:22.500,0:12:24.400
Then tell me your reasons.

0:12:27.140,0:12:28.760
Think about it this way -

0:12:30.900,0:12:32.780
in order to appease Nian Gengyao,

0:12:33.480,0:12:36.040
His Majesty will reinstate Nian Shilan sooner or later,

0:12:36.840,0:12:38.700
at least her honorary name,

0:12:39.920,0:12:44.440
if not promoting her to Noble Consort, depending on the situation in court.

0:12:46.140,0:12:48.360
Even if the Empress Dowager favors you,

0:12:48.500,0:12:50.640
you can't hold your ground against Consort Nian.

0:12:51.060,0:12:52.460
Instead of watching that situation unfold,

0:12:52.740,0:12:54.020
I chose to be the person who suggested it

0:12:55.220,0:12:59.060
because His Majesty knows he has no choice, and 
now will also feel guilty when he reinstates her.

0:12:59.900,0:13:01.580
As such feelings grow,

0:13:01.700,0:13:03.600
my position will be more stable.

0:13:04.260,0:13:06.560
You've explained it very clearly

0:13:06.800,0:13:08.840
but why am I still so confused?

0:13:09.080,0:13:13.300
With her title of Consort restored, won't it be even
easier for her to become a Noble Consort?

0:13:13.620,0:13:15.740
You may have calculated your moves,

0:13:15.880,0:13:18.500
but she won't necessarily act as you expect.

0:13:21.060,0:13:22.220
You're right.

0:13:24.360,0:13:26.140
I don't know when it was

0:13:26.720,0:13:30.480
that I became this calculating and selfish.

0:13:31.380,0:13:32.400
I know

0:13:33.960,0:13:36.400
I’m no longer the kind and innocent person I was.

0:13:36.900,0:13:38.300
But I did so

0:13:39.940,0:13:42.340
for reasons that are not easy to explain right now.

0:13:42.380,0:13:43.760
All right, all right.

0:13:43.760,0:13:46.940
You can have your reasons and I have my confusion.

0:13:47.700,0:13:50.200
"Half a sentence is too much conversation if poorly timed."

0:13:54.180,0:13:57.420
Is it because you want to use Consort Fleur to curry favor with Nian Genyao

0:13:57.680,0:14:00.180
because you've seen Nian Gengyao’s power grow?

0:14:03.160,0:14:04.420
Meizhuang,

0:14:05.440,0:14:07.400
am I so despicable in your eyes?

0:14:09.280,0:14:11.000
I have never forgotten

0:14:11.620,0:14:14.120
how I lost my child that day.

0:14:16.280,0:14:17.020
Huan’er,

0:14:18.440,0:14:20.440
we grew up together.

0:14:21.340,0:14:25.440
I've always known that my looks and wits
fade in comparison to you.

0:14:26.240,0:14:29.320
So I decided to cultivate my virtue and modesty.

0:14:30.280,0:14:33.160
You were good at dancing, so I focused on the zither.

0:14:33.940,0:14:36.040
My skills were never inferior to yours.

0:14:36.920,0:14:39.820
Then, we were selected to enter the palace together.

0:14:40.100,0:14:42.620
We always supported each other.

0:14:43.460,0:14:46.580
Even though His Majesty no longer favors me,

0:14:48.420,0:14:50.860
I never resented you in the least.

0:14:52.220,0:14:54.460
But I don’t know why,

0:14:55.340,0:14:56.980
looking at you now,

0:14:58.040,0:15:00.340
I feel that I’m so far behind.

0:15:02.040,0:15:03.980
You have Dr. Wen’s admiration

0:15:04.720,0:15:06.440
and His Majesty’s favor.

0:15:07.800,0:15:10.880
Your father has received honors from His Majesty.

0:15:11.980,0:15:14.260
Everything is going well for you.

0:15:16.020,0:15:17.360
But I ...

0:15:19.540,0:15:21.840
I have nothing.

0:15:23.760,0:15:25.760
I remember when we were little,

0:15:26.440,0:15:29.460
we set off paper boats into the river together.

0:15:30.580,0:15:32.200
The nursemaid said

0:15:32.260,0:15:34.360
the further the boats traveled,

0:15:34.960,0:15:37.400
the further from home we would marry.

0:15:38.260,0:15:39.780
But you said

0:15:40.600,0:15:43.620
both our boats had to travel the same distance

0:15:44.020,0:15:45.980
So we would marry in the same place -

0:15:46.400,0:15:48.220
ideally to two brothers.

0:15:48.760,0:15:51.360
Then we could stay together for the rest of our lives.

0:15:53.480,0:15:57.020
We are in the same place now.

0:15:58.520,0:16:00.880
But I never imagined our hearts could drift so far.

0:16:01.980,0:16:03.020
Meizhuang,

0:16:04.660,0:16:06.920
do you really intend to drift apart?

0:16:09.060,0:16:11.440
"Even the best banquet must come to an end."

0:16:12.200,0:16:14.560
It isn't a matter of drifting or not.

0:16:17.220,0:16:18.440
You can leave now,

0:16:19.080,0:16:21.080
and you need not visit if not necessary.

0:16:24.400,0:16:26.380
You will understand me one day.

0:16:27.500,0:16:28.960
Perhaps.

0:16:30.860,0:16:32.280
Meizhuang,

0:16:34.000,0:16:35.800
since you don’t wish to be disturbed,

0:16:38.500,0:16:41.140
I won't return until my goal is achieved.

0:17:14.120,0:17:16.920
Peace and grace to Your Majesty

0:17:17.920,0:17:20.440
- Peace to Your Highnesses.
- Rise.

0:17:20.920,0:17:21.840
I thank Your Majesty.

0:17:23.480,0:17:25.320
It's nice that Lady Vertu is here as well.

0:17:25.320,0:17:27.680
I have not seen you together for a while.

0:17:30.440,0:17:31.920
I've been serving the Empress Dowager,

0:17:31.920,0:17:33.620
so I rarely venture to other palaces.

0:17:34.020,0:17:37.260
It's about time for Her Majesty to take her medicine.

0:17:38.360,0:17:40.340
Please allow me to take my leave.

0:17:41.140,0:17:41.940
All right.

0:17:42.540,0:17:45.200
I'm glad Her Majesty likes you. 
You should visit her as much as possible.

0:17:54.120,0:17:56.060
Concubine Sourire, why don't you take a seat?

0:17:58.580,0:18:01.260
Lady Vertu has been behaving like that
to everyone recently.

0:18:01.460,0:18:02.960
Don't let it worry you.

0:18:03.140,0:18:04.880
Perhaps it is because of the weather

0:18:05.300,0:18:07.400
that Meizhuang has not been in good health?

0:18:07.600,0:18:09.640
The weather would not cause anything serious.

0:18:09.760,0:18:11.180
But women are fragile

0:18:11.420,0:18:12.980
and need to be taken better care of.

0:18:13.400,0:18:14.820
Don't be like Consort Honnête -

0:18:14.820,0:18:16.760
she began to have great trouble with her health.

0:18:16.840,0:18:17.800
Yes.

0:18:18.100,0:18:19.400
His Majesty told me that

0:18:19.400,0:18:21.920
you haven't seen your family since you entered the palace.

0:18:22.280,0:18:25.380
I've arranged for your mother to visit you today.

0:18:25.580,0:18:27.320
You can wait in the Palace of Pearl Jade.

0:18:29.060,0:18:30.640
I thank Your Majesty.

0:18:32.160,0:18:33.780
Go get ready for her visit.

0:18:33.860,0:18:36.600
Your mother and sister will arrive in the afternoon.

0:18:36.900,0:18:37.860
Yes.

0:18:38.920,0:18:40.560
Well then, you're all dismissed.

0:18:42.340,0:18:44.140
Lady An, please stay behind.

0:18:44.740,0:18:45.520
Yes.

0:18:47.280,0:18:49.120
I bid Your Majesty goodbye.

0:19:01.780,0:19:02.820
Your Majesty.

0:19:02.920,0:19:04.740
You saw what happened just now, right?

0:19:05.960,0:19:08.200
Lady Vertu and Concubine Sourire
behave like strangers in the street.

0:19:08.720,0:19:10.500
Lady Vertu has a decent family background.

0:19:10.520,0:19:12.740
And Concubine Sourire's father has been
 promoted several times.

0:19:12.860,0:19:14.800
If they were united,

0:19:15.000,0:19:17.380
I'm afraid it would only cause more trouble in the palace.

0:19:17.440,0:19:18.980
I agree with Your Majesty.

0:19:19.060,0:19:22.820
It would not be desirable if both Lady Vertu and Concubine 
Sourire gained as much power as Consort Fleur.

0:19:23.060,0:19:25.060
I'm of the same mind.

0:19:26.240,0:19:28.680
His Majesty can favor anyone he likes,

0:19:29.040,0:19:32.200
but we can't allow a second Consort Fleur.

0:19:38.100,0:19:41.100
Mother, why are we still not at Huan's palace?

0:19:41.500,0:19:42.800
Don't complain.

0:19:42.960,0:19:44.680
We're in the Forbidden City.

0:19:44.840,0:19:46.940
There's nowhere under heaven bigger than this.

0:19:47.100,0:19:48.600
That's why it's a long trip.

0:19:48.600,0:19:50.620
Don't say anything foolish when you see your sister.

0:19:50.840,0:19:51.820
Do you understand?

